data.title: List of Movies and Specials/YTV
authors: Contributors to YTV Schedule Archives Wiki
data.meta_description: The following is a list of movies and specials that have aired since YTV's inception in 1988. The list includes each movie/special's premiere date (or earliest known airdate), as well as their final airing (or last known airdate) on the network. Please note that the list is currently a work in...
